  <h2>üéØ Adversaries</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Scattered Spider is targeting VMware ESXi hypervisors using advanced social engineering and disk-swap attacks to deploy ransomware. Google urges vSphere hardening and phishing-resistant MFA. <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/scattered-spider-is-running-a-vmware-esxi-hacking-spree/" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
