    <li>The BlackSuit ransomware site was seized in a global law enforcement op. Linked to Royal and Conti, BlackSuit used phishing and credential theft, demanding ransoms up to $60M. <a href="https://securityaffairs.com/180409/cyber-crime/law-enforcement-operations-seized-blacksuit-ransomware-gangs-darknet-sites.html" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
